with proximal branch (arrowed) branched to two orders and bearing rachillae with staminate flowers only. Bottom left—infructescence of 
<taxonomicName class="Liliopsida" family="Arecaceae" genus="Areca" kingdom="Plantae" order="Arecales" pageId="1" pageNumber="35" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="songthanensis">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="35">A. songthanensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
